                <span style="font-size:.68rem;color:rgba(245,239,230,.82);font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;">Managing savings</span>
                <span style="font-size:.58rem;background:rgba(16,185,129,.15);color:#10b981;padding:.1rem .4rem;border-radius:4px;font-weight:600;font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;">Both agree ✓</span>
              </div>
            </div>
