            <div style="font-family:'Playfair Display',Georgia,serif;font-size:2.2rem;font-weight:700;color:white;line-height:.95;margin-bottom:.65rem;letter-spacing:-.02em;">The Mismatch</div>
            <p style="font-size:.8rem;color:#E91E63;font-weight:600;line-height:1.45;margin:0;font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;">Different conflict clocks. Knowing that changes everything.</p>
